        "created_at": "2018-01-29T02:29:49.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/wine.asp?iWine=2906870\"><strong>1979 Henri Boillot Savigny-l\u00e8s-Beaune 1er Cru Les Vergelesses</strong></a> <em>- France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Beaune, Savigny-l\u00e8s-Beaune 1er Cru (1/28/2018)</em><br>\nTertiary nose of reducing meats, decaying roses, black earth and pine needles. It is sweet and vinous with a light ginger like pepper character. There\u2019s plenty going on and a tangy line of acidity keeps everything fresh. Not particularly deep or long but certainly engaging.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
