        "name": "Dennis Atick",
        "username": "Dennis_Atick",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/dennis_atick/{size}/429_2.png",
        "created_at": "2018-01-29T11:12:07.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Yes. Very cool. I often wonder about Boillot reds, not of this age, but in general, as I only ever pay attention to the whites. The pinots seem to to get decent praise, at least current vintages. This sounds like a nice treat.<br>\nThanks, Jeremy.</p>",
